How to build images:
cd lesson-10
./build_images

docker compose: docker-compose up -d
docker compose: docker-compose stop

postgres setup:
mkdir $HOME/docker/volumes/postgres

slack bot setup:
copy .env file to ~/.slack/ directory and fill it there
For slack bot - use this article as an example https://towardsdatascience.com/develop-a-slack-bot-using-golang-1025b3e606bc
Slash commands:
Get last known temperature for a city
/weather get <city>
Get all known weathers for all cities
/weather list
Go to openweather privider, get weather for a city and save it in DB
/weather fetch <city>
For openweather - register here https://openweathermap.org and get the token
